<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.1.5">
<l>nīrēṟu ceñcaṭainī lakaṇṭaṉum nāṉmukaṉum muṟaiyāl</l>
<l>cīrēṟu vācakañ ceyyaniṉṟa tirumālai nāṭutirēl</l>
<l>vārēṟu koṅkai yuruppiṇiyai valiyap piṭittukoṇṭu</l>
<l>tērēṟṟi cēṉainaṭu vupōrceyyac cikkeṉakkaṇ ṭāruḷar.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you seek Tirumāl who remained when</l>
<l>he with the blue throat and red matted locks</l>
<l rend="indent">from which waters rise</l>
<l>and the four-faced one performed words of praise</l>
<l rend="indent">abounding in excellence by turns,</l>
<l>there are those who certainly saw him when,</l>
<l rend="indent">doing battle in the midst of the army,</l>
<l>[he] forcefully seized and took Rukmiṇī,</l>
<l rend="indent">with breast swelling from [her] bodice,</l>
<l>[and] put [her] in [his] chariot.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
